<p>I'm using <a href="https://github.com/dsanel/mongoose-delete" rel="nofollow">mongoose-delete</a> plugin.</p>  <p>I want to build a simple <a href="http://mongoosejs.com/docs/middleware.html" rel="nofollow">mongoose middleware</a> so I add <code>{deleted:false}</code>to every <code>find</code> query on that schema. </p>  <pre><code>var mongoose = require('mongoose'),     mongooseDelete = require('mongoose-delete'),     Schema = mongoose.Schema;  var MySchema = new Schema({   name: {type: String, required: true} });  MySchema.plugin(mongooseDelete, {deletedAt: true, deletedBy: true});  MySchema.pre('find', function (next){   // I want to add {deleted: false} to the queries conditions }); </code></pre>  <p>How should I implement the pre-find middleware?</p>